## Geco How-to

### Workflow for a race
- copy a virgin set of data templates
- use a spreadsheet application to fill in templates with course data, runners registration, etc.
- launch Geco and follow the flow of tabbed panes (from left to right)

When you launch a Geco application, it first opens a file window so that you can choose a folder with existing data.

